{"tid":130952,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"原來對焦屏咁化學","createTime":"2017-02-22T17:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T14:50:24.000Z","uid":5277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed2fb15dc232a7a3267f81c5d0fccd1e4cc0c0e0","tid":130952,"uid":5277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"部80d觀景窗望出去有塵，諗住自己搞。<br />\n用air blower 唔得再用埋個除塵掃，點知搞完仲衰。<br />\n寄返廠先知原來整花左個對焦屏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再上網查下先知原來對焦屏好脆弱，最好避免任何接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWhy to never touch that focusing screen：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/amp/s/thefoxtakespictures.com/2015/08/31/why-to-never-touch-that-focusing-screen/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.uk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fthefoxtakespictures.com%2F2015%2F08%2F31%2Fwhy-to-never-touch-that-focusing-screen%2Famp%2F&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e24b2410\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.co.uk/amp/s/thefoxtakespictures.com/2015/08/31/why-to-never-touch-that-focusing-screen/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"112c5d26b4e9bb2634c3cc8eae155588176b2f7c","tid":130952,"uid":20669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T00:24:28.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，我搵唔到pm功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以問你係英國轉p牌啲野？<br />\n你講既比齊証件係咪淨係張暫准牌？佢會唔會收左？同埋駛唔駛有信證明係香港考牌？<br />\n因為好多大陸人咁轉好似話英國發現漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5806cd249a2396ebde393ba4ca557563c054a9","tid":130952,"uid":5277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好意思，我搵唔到pm功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以問你係英國轉p牌啲野？<br />\n你講既比齊証件係咪淨係張暫准牌？佢會唔會收左？同埋駛唔駛有信證明係香港考牌？<br />\n因為好多大陸人咁轉好似話英國發現漏洞<img 